FBIS4-46225 "jptot023__l94011" JPRS-TOT-94-023-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 31 May 1994 EAST ASIA JAPAN Rightist Fires Into Air Near Former PM Hosokawa Rightist Fires Into Air Near Former PM Hosokawa Police Raid Right-Wing Group OW3105073194 Tokyo KYODO in English 0713 GMT 31 May 94 OW3105073194 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, May 31 KYODO -- Police Tuesday [31 May] started raiding a right-wing organization's office and some other locations in connection with Monday's gunshot fired near former Prime Minister Morihiro Hosokawa, police said. Police are searching the Shinjuku office of the right-wing group "Shokonjuku" on suspicion of violating the law to control the possession of firearms and swords. [passage omitted]
